_sText: * If you have, or plan to use this map on a server please let me know! * GG_Crackshot_Final presented by: Crackshot This is my second gungame map sticking with the more "Arena" style of gun game maps, please make sure to leave me any information on bugs, glitches, or any other issues you have with the map on this page. Edit: I have resubmitted the map file with 2 versions of the map a Dev texture version for all you FPS whores and picky players out there and the textured version, ive tested both versions and have found no changes in FPS but i will leave the choice on which is used up to you.
